"setlocale(LC_MESSAGES, \"\") so callers don't depend on the POSIX module "
"either."
msgstr ""
"如果存在 Locale::gettext，则此封装器还调用 setlocale(LC_MESSAGES, \"\")，因此"
"调用者也不依赖于 POSIX 模块。"

