"and drop these first 2 array items.  Here, the reference is provided by a "
"string C<< $filename:$linenum >>."
msgstr ""
"此函数从数组 C<< @{$self->{TT}{doc_in}} >> 返回要解析的第一行及其对应的引用 "
"(打包为数组)，并删除前两个数组项。这里，引用由字符串 C<< $filename:$linenum "
">> 提供。"

